name: Taradale McDonald's (Maccas)

comment: There is a main door that leads to a room where theres the males on the left, womens on the right and a wheelchair option/gender neutral option. I do believe it's a safe space either way if you go into the binary bathrooms. The rooms are small with about 2 stalls in each bathroom. The wheelchair/gender neutral bathroom is big (obviously) and no one can disturb you in there.

name: Taradale McDonalds (maccas)
